head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths KINNE, FRANCES P.

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths KINNE, FRANCES P.

block.p: KINNE-Frances P. (nee Paytas). Age 62 a long-time resident of Tenafly, NJ passed away on October 11, 2000. Beloved Mother of Lisa of Tenafly, NJ Jonathan of Tenafly, NJ and James of Somerville, Massachusetts. Dear Daughter of John of Jersey City, NJ. Dear Sister of Helen and Victoria, both of Jersey City, NJ and Mary of Hazlet, NJ. Also survived by several nieces and nephews. Friends may call at the Barrett Funeral home 148 Dean Dr. Tenafly, NJ on Friday 2-4 & 7-9 PM. Funeral Mass Saturday 11AM Mt. Carmel Church Tenafly, New Jersey. Interment Private. In lieu of flowers donations may be payable to Columbia University Bartoli Brain Tumor Laboratory. Checks are to be given to the family.
